Operations Manager, Liam Clarke shares how the idea was sparked by a concept called &#8216;speed by illusion&#8217;. Cardboard cut-outs of Tshwane Metro Police Department cars spotted along the N1 toll route between Pretoria and Bela Bela, and the N4 toll route highways are part of an Easter road safety campaign. The Bakwena Platinum Corridor Concessionaire is the brainchild behind the campaign. Operations Manager, Liam Clarke shares how the idea was sparked by a concept called speed by illusion . Click below to listen to the full interview...